Willard;;2003;;PG-13;;Drama,Horror,Thriller;;6.1;;Glen Morgan;;Crispin Glover,R. Lee Ermey,Laura Harring,Jackie Burroughs,Ashlyn Gere,William S. Taylor,Edward Horn,Gus Lynch,Laara Sadiq,David Parker,Ty Olsson,Kristen Cloke;;This is the story of Willard Stiles who is a social misfit taking care of his ill and fragile but verbally abusive mother Henrietta in a musty old mansion that is also home to a colony of rats. Willard then finds himself constantly humiliated in front of his co-workers and is eventually fired by his cruel and uncaring boss, Mr. Frank Martin, a vicious man whose professional interest in Willard extends to a personal financial one.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0310357/